# DroidPhotos — Cursor Agent Rules

This project has 8 documentation files in the root folder. Read all of them
before taking any action, in this order:
1. AGENTS.md (read this first — its rules govern everything)
2. README.md
3. ARCHITECTURE.md
4. DECISIONS.md
5. PRD.md
6. TASKS.md
7. UI_SPEC.md
8. API_SETUP.md

## Non-negotiable rules:
- Never write or change code without first explaining your plan and getting
  explicit approval from the user
- Never delete local photos
- Never touch Google Photos albums this app did not create
- When in doubt, stop and ask — never assume
- Work through TASKS.md in order, one task at a time
- You are working with a beginner — explain every decision in plain English